Package com.pb.sawdust.tabledata.read

Provides classes for creating data tables from external sources.

See: Description

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    SubTableReader
    The SubTableReader interface provides a framework through which subtables (parts of a table) may be read from an external data source.
    TableReader
    The TableReader interface is used to read table data from external data sources.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    AbstractSubTableReader
    The AbstractSubTableReader is a skeletal SubTableReader easing the programming burden on sub-table reader implementations.
    AbstractTableReader
    The AbstractTableReader class is a skeletal implementation of TableReader easing the programming burden on table reader implementations.
    CsvTableReader
    The CsvTableReader is a delimited data table reader used with comma-separated value (CSV) files.
    DbfTableReader
    The DbfTableReader class is a TableReader which reads DBF (dBase-format) files into data tables.
    DelimitedTextTableReader
    The DelimitedTextTableReader class allows data tables to be read from delimited data text files.
    FileTableReader
    The FileTableReader class provides a simple TableReader implementation for use when data tables are to be read from files.
    FixedWidthTextTableReader
    The FixedWidthTextTableReader is used to read text files with fixed width columns.
    MultiTextTableReader<S,R extends TextFileTableReader<S>>
    The MultiTextTableReader class provides a TextFileTableReader implementation wherein multiple data tables can be read from a single file.
    TableReaderFactory
    The TableReaderFactory class provides static convenience methods for creating TableReaders.
    TextFileTableReader<S>
    The TextFileTableReader class is a base class for reading table data from text files.
    WhitespaceDelimitedTextTableReader
    The WhitespaceDelimitedTableReader is a table data reader for text files whose column entries are delimited by whitespace.
  • Enum Summary 
    Enum Description
    ReaderType
    The ReaderType enum is used to hold information about all known TableReader classes.
